Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": ["Hello"],
  "target_lang": "invalid_lang",
  "source_lang": "en"
}

### Missing required field
POST {{baseUrl}}/translate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": ["Hello"]
}

### Invalid beam size (too small)
